title: Paul McCartney - Off The Ground 5.1 DTS Upmix
description:
Paul McCartney - Off The Ground 5.1 DTS Upmix

This cd was created using Adobe Audition 1.5 and SurCode DTS version 1.0.21. The bin and cue files were generated by PowerISO 4.4.

The files were ripped from the original cd to wav files then Adobe Audition was used to create the 6 channels. Finally, SurCode was used to encode to DTS surround sound.

I checked this out on my surround system and all 6 speakers are active.

Please leave a comment after you listen to this and let me know what you think. This is my first cd conversion to 5.1 DTS surround cd. I solicit constructive criticism, but please don't flame. 


This sounds great crancked up on my surround stereo so I thought I would share this with this community. 

Enjoy.

Note: You must have a surround sound system with DTS decoder to play this.
